  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 8th level, you can emit a 30-foot aura to either ward off or welcome emotional influence for a number of rounds per day equal to your wizard level. If you choose to ward, you and your allies within this aura receive a +4&nbsp;<em>morale bonus</em>&nbsp;on saves against mind-affecting spells and effects, and any fear effects targeting you or your allies are reduced by one step (<em>shaken</em>&nbsp;has no effect,&nbsp;<em>frightened</em>&nbsp;becomes&nbsp;<em>shaken</em>, and&nbsp;<em>panicked</em>&nbsp;becomes&nbsp;<em>frightened</em>). If you chose to enhance emotional influence, enemies within the aura receive a â€“2 penalty on saves against mind-affecting spells and effects. These rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>"
    },
